<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Container Usage Alert</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #333;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      }
      h2 {
        color: #007BFF;
      }
      .info {
        margin: 10px 0;
      }
      .label {
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>🚨 Container Usage Alert</h2>
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>Here's the latest usage report for your container:</p>

      <div class="info"><span class="label">📦 Container ID:</span> {{containerId}}</div>
      <div class="info"><span class="label">📁 Path:</span> {{pathName}}</div>
      <div class="info"><span class="label">💾 Total Space:</span> {{totalSpace}}</div>
      <div class="info"><span class="label">📊 Used Space:</span> {{usedSpace}}</div>
      <div class="info"><span class="label">🟢 Free Space:</span> {{freeSpace}}</div>

      <p>Please take appropriate actions if the usage is nearing critical levels.</p>

      <p>Regards,<br/>Your Monitoring Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
